root: ^Shiver me timbers, ye actually did it!
^Very well, ye can have your family back.
^As for you slaves, you'll be spendin' the rest of ya days aboard the Flying Dutchbug scrubbing me mandibles and cooking up some grub!
^But I have a wife and 300 children!
^Why would you do this?! I thought this was a friendship, not a slave ship!
